<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
[a]:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Prednji dio vozila
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<c-change/>
<servinfosub id = "AHRAP70A3406002002">
<title>
Ugradnja
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AHRAP70A3406003">Provjera kardanskog vratila</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AHRAP70A3406004">Rastavljanje i sastavljanje sklopa kardanskog vratila</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Obrnite postupak uklanjanja da biste ugradili kardansko vratilo, imajući na umu sljedeće.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Kada postavite kardansko vratilo, poravnajte označena mjesta (1). U protivnom može doći do vibracija u vožnji.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Vijke oslonca kardanskog vratila br. 1 i matice oslonca središnjeg ležaja zategnite propisanim momentom pritezanja.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
<torque>
<torqueitem id = "T3D001">
<t-part>
Vijak kardanskog vratila br.1
</t-part>
<t-part1>
a
</t-part1>
<t-value1>
23
</t-value1>
<t-value2>
2,3
</t-value2>
<t-value3>
17,0
</t-value3>
</torqueitem>
<torqueitem id = "T3D002">
<t-part>
Matica oslonca središnjeg ležaja
</t-part>
<t-part1>
b
</t-part1>
<t-value1>
50
</t-value1>
<t-value2>
5,1
</t-value2>
<t-value3>
37,0
</t-value3>
</torqueitem>
</torque>
